import { ApplicationConfig } from '@angular/core';

 export const appConfig: ApplicationConfig = { providers: [], };
app.component.html:
<style>
.control-section{
    margin-top: 100px;
}
</style>
<style>
    .diagram-print-export .e-bigger #toolbarEditor .e-icons.e-caret,
    .diagram-print-export #toolbarEditor .e-icons.e-caret {
        font-size: 12px;
        margin-right: 0px;
    }

    .diagram-print-export #custombtn {
        padding: 4px 0px 2px 4px;
    }

    @font-face {
        font-family: 'e-ddb-icons';
        src: url(data:application/x-font-ttf;charset=utf-8;base64,) format('truetype');
        font-weight: normal;
        font-style: normal;
    }

    .e-ddb-icons {
        font-family: 'e-ddb-icons';
        speak: none;
        font-size: 55px;
        font-style: normal;
        font-weight: normal;
        font-variant: normal;
        text-transform: none;
        line-height: 1;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }

    .diagram-print-export .e-print::before {
        content: "\e70e";
    }

    .diagram-print-export .e-export::before {
        content: "\e711";
    }

    .diagram-print-export .material .e-print::before {
        content: "\e703";
    }

    .diagram-print-export .material .e-export::before {
        content: "\e706";
    }

    .diagram-print-export .bootstrap .e-print::before {
        content: "\e71b";
    }

    .diagram-print-export .bootstrap .e-export::before {
        content: "\e71e";
    }
</style>
<div class="control-section diagram-print-export">
    <ejs-toolbar id='toolbarEditor' #toolbarEditor overflowMode='Scrollable' (clicked)='onItemClick($event)'>
        <e-items>
            <e-item>
                <ng-template #template>
                    <button ejs-dropdownbutton [items]='exportTypes' iconCss='e-ddb-icons e-export' content='Export' (select)='onSelectExportFormat($event)'></button>
                </ng-template>
            </e-item>
            <e-item type='Button' text='Print' prefixIcon='e-ddb-icons  e-print'>
            </e-item>
            <e-item>
                <ng-template #template>
                    <ejs-checkbox label="Multiple Page" [(checked)]="multiplePage"></ejs-checkbox>
                </ng-template>
            </e-item>
        </e-items>
    </ejs-toolbar>
    <div style="width: 100%;">
        <ejs-diagram #diagram id="diagram" width="100%" height="580px" [getConnectorDefaults]=getConnectorDefaults [snapSettings]=snapSettings
            (created)="create($event)">
            <e-nodes>
                <e-node id='sourceNode1' [width]=100 [height]=50 [offsetX]=320 [offsetY]=100 [style]='style'>
                    <e-node-annotations>
                        <e-node-annotation content='Source Document' [margin]=margin>
                        </e-node-annotation>
                    </e-node-annotations>
                </e-node>
                <e-node id='censusNode2' [width]=100 [height]=75 [offsetX]=320 [offsetY]=225 [shape]='shape1' [style]='style1'>
                    <e-node-annotations>
                        <e-node-annotation content='Census Record' [margin]=margin>
                        </e-node-annotation>
                    </e-node-annotations>
                </e-node>
                <e-node id='booksNode3' [width]=100 [height]=75 [offsetX]=320 [offsetY]=350 [shape]='shape1' [style]='style1'>
                    <e-node-annotations>
                        <e-node-annotation content='Books and Magazine'>
                        </e-node-annotation>
                    </e-node-annotations>
                </e-node>
                <e-node id='recordNode4' [width]=125 [height]=50 [offsetX]=520 [offsetY]=225 [style]='style'>
                    <e-node-annotations>
                        <e-node-annotation content='Record Template'>
                        </e-node-annotation>
                    </e-node-annotations>
                </e-node>
                <e-node id='traditionalNode5' [width]=125 [height]=50 [offsetX]=520 [offsetY]=350 [style]='style'>
                    <e-node-annotations>
                        <e-node-annotation content='Traditional Template'>
                        </e-node-annotation>
                    </e-node-annotations>
                </e-node>
                <e-node id='nontraditionalNode6' [width]=135 [height]=50 [offsetX]=320 [offsetY]=450 [style]='style'>
                    <e-node-annotations>
                        <e-node-annotation content='Nontraditional'>
                        </e-node-annotation>
                    </e-node-annotations>
                </e-node>
                <e-node id='Radial1' [width]=125 [height]=50 [offsetX]=1000 [offsetY]=250 [shape]='ellipse' [style]='radialstyle'>
                    <e-node-annotations>
                        <e-node-annotation content='Health Fitness'>
                        </e-node-annotation>
                    </e-node-annotations>
                </e-node>
                <e-node id='Radial2' [width]=125 [height]=75 [offsetX]=1000 [offsetY]=125 [shape]='ellipse' [style]='radialstyle1'>
                    <e-node-annotations>
                        <e-node-annotation content='Diet'>
                        </e-node-annotation>
                    </e-node-annotations>
                </e-node>
                <e-node id='Radial3' [width]=125 [height]=75 [offsetX]=1175 [offsetY]=200 [shape]=ellipse [style]=radialstyle1>
                    <e-node-annotations>
                        <e-node-annotation content='Flexibility'>
                        </e-node-annotation>
                    </e-node-annotations>
                </e-node>
                <e-node id='Radial4' [width]=125 [height]=75 [offsetX]=1150 [offsetY]=375 [shape]=ellipse [style]=radialstyle1>
                    <e-node-annotations>
                        <e-node-annotation content='Muscular Endurance'>
                        </e-node-annotation>
                    </e-node-annotations>
                </e-node>
                <e-node id='Radial5' [width]=125 [height]=75 [offsetX]=825 [offsetY]=200 [shape]=ellipse [style]=radialstyle1>
                    <e-node-annotations>
                        <e-node-annotation content='Cardiovascular Strength'>
                        </e-node-annotation>
                    </e-node-annotations>
                </e-node>
                <e-node id='Radial6' [width]=125 [height]=75 [offsetX]=920 [offsetY]=375 [shape]=ellipse [style]=radialstyle1>
                    <e-node-annotations>
                        <e-node-annotation content='Muscular Strength'>
                        </e-node-annotation>
                    </e-node-annotations>
                </e-node>
            </e-nodes>
            <e-connectors>
                <e-connector id='flowChartConnector1' sourceID='sourceNode1' targetID='censusNode2'>
                </e-connector>
                <e-connector id='flowChartConnector2' sourceID='censusNode2' targetID='booksNode3'>
                    <e-connector-annotations>
                        <e-connector-annotation content='No' [style]='annotationTextStyle'>
                        </e-connector-annotation>
                    </e-connector-annotations>
                </e-connector>
                <e-connector id='flowChartConnector3' sourceID='booksNode3' targetID='nontraditionalNode6'>
                    <e-connector-annotations>
                        <e-connector-annotation content='No' [style]='annotationTextStyle'>
                        </e-connector-annotation>
                    </e-connector-annotations>
                </e-connector>
                <e-connector id='flowChartConnector4' sourceID='censusNode2' targetID='recordNode4'>
                    <e-connector-annotations>
                        <e-connector-annotation content='Yes' [style]='annotationTextStyle'>
                        </e-connector-annotation>
                    </e-connector-annotations>
                </e-connector>
                <e-connector id='flowChartConnector5' sourceID='booksNode3' targetID='traditionalNode5'>
                    <e-connector-annotations>
                        <e-connector-annotation content='Yes' [style]='annotationTextStyle'>
                        </e-connector-annotation>
                    </e-connector-annotations>
                </e-connector>
                <e-connector id='RadialConnector1' sourceID='Radial1' targetID='Radial2'>
                    <e-connector-annotations>
                        <e-connector-annotation content='Yes' [style]='annotationTextStyle'>
                        </e-connector-annotation>
                    </e-connector-annotations>
                </e-connector>
                <e-connector id='RadialConnector2' sourceID='Radial1' targetID='Radial3'>
                    <e-connector-annotations>
                        <e-connector-annotation content='Yes' [style]='annotationTextStyle'>
                        </e-connector-annotation>
                    </e-connector-annotations>
                </e-connector>
                <e-connector id='RadialConnector3' sourceID='Radial1' targetID='Radial4'>
                    <e-connector-annotations>
                        <e-connector-annotation content='Yes' [style]='annotationTextStyle'>
                        </e-connector-annotation>
                    </e-connector-annotations>
                </e-connector>
                <e-connector id='RadialConnector4' sourceID='Radial1' targetID='Radial5'>
                    <e-connector-annotations>
                        <e-connector-annotation content='Yes' [style]='annotationTextStyle'>
                        </e-connector-annotation>
                    </e-connector-annotations>
                </e-connector>
                <e-connector id='RadialConnector5' sourceID='Radial1' targetID='Radial6'>
                    <e-connector-annotations>
                        <e-connector-annotation content='Yes' [style]='annotationTextStyle'>
                        </e-connector-annotation>
                    </e-connector-annotations>
                </e-connector>
            </e-connectors>
        </ejs-diagram>
    </div>
</div>
